emp dir in `RunPrompt` and `StartSession`\\n- Verify `CLAUDE_CONFIG_DIR` (already set by test harness for Claude tests) also blocks OpenCode from reading `~/.claude/CLAUDE.md` — if not, handle separately\\n- No auth files needed (API key comes from env var)\\n\\n### Files\\n- `e2e/agents/opencode.go`\\n\\n## Task 3: Verify isolation\\n\\n> Status: todo\\n\\n### Acceptance\\n- Local run with custom `~/.gemini/GEMINI.md` and `~/.config/opencode/AGENTS.md` does not affect test behavior\\n- CI continues to pass\\n\",\"structuredPatch\":[{\"oldStart\":31,\"oldLines\":6,\"newStart\":31,\"newLines\":7,\"lines\":[\" ### Fix\",\" - Set `OPENCODE_CONFIG_DIR` to a clean temp dir in `RunPrompt` and `StartSession`\",\" - Verify `CLAUDE_CONFIG_DIR` (already set by test harness for Claude tests) also blocks OpenCode from reading `~/.claude/CLAUDE.md` — if not, handle separately\",\"+- May need to seed config in Bootstrap (similar to Claude's `hasCompletedOnboarding`) so OpenCode doesn't show first-run setup prompts when config dir is empty\",\" - No auth files needed (API key comes from env var)\",\" \",\" ### Files\"]}],\"userModified\":false,\"replaceAll\":false},\"sourceToolAssistantUUID\":\"b6f337d6-b41a-408a-a25c-a153bda24883\"}\n{\"parentUuid\":\"4377046d-e51c-4f81-a553-1858f91d5d36\",\"isSidechain\":false,\"userType\":\"external\",\"cwd\":\"/Users/alex/workspace/cli\",\"sessionId\":\"d9f0a13a-2256-4ef2-a6ed-7fe605e55655\",\"version\":\"2.1.58\",\"gitBranch\":\"alex/more-e2e-fixes\",\"slug\":\"ticklish-zooming-robin\",\"message\":{\"model\":\"claude-opus-4-6\",\"id\":\"msg_01Y1YNW1hEsKBVzwAnrHS5W9\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Done.\"}],\"stop_reason\":null,\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":428,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":84096,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":428},\"output_tokens\":1,\"service_tier\":\"standard\",\"in